flowchart LR
    RAW["Raw event"]
    L1["L1 Heuristic\n(rule-based)"]
    L2["L2 SimHash\n(near-duplicate)"]
    L3["L3 FastText\n(spam / human)"]
    CLEAN["Clean event\n(PASS)"]
    DROP["Dropped\n(DROP)"]

    RAW --> L1
    L1 -->|PASS| L2
    L1 -->|DROP| DROP
    L2 -->|PASS| L3
    L2 -->|DROP| DROP
    L3 -->|PASS| CLEAN
    L3 -->|DROP| DROP
